Package com.whirvis.jraknet.discovery

Components used to discover RakNet servers on both local and external networks.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DiscoveryListener
    Used to listen for events that occur in the Discovery system.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DiscoveredServer
    Represents a server that has been discovered by the Discovery system.
    Discovery
    Used to discover servers on the local network and on external networks.
    DiscoveryHandler
    Used by the Discovery system with the sole purpose of sending received packets to the discovery system so they can be handled.
    DiscoveryThread
    Used by the Discovery system to server pings in the background.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DiscoveryMode
    Determines how discovery will be handled by the Discovery system.

Package com.whirvis.jraknet.discovery Description

Components used to discover RakNet servers on both local and external networks.
